[[File:Yoda_Statue.jpg|thumb|Noble's statue of [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] at [[Letterman Digital Arts Center]].]]
'''Lawrence Noble''' is the artist who sculpted the statue of [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] on display at [[Lucasfilm Ltd.|Lucasfilm's]] [[Letterman Digital Arts Center]]. He created a lifesize bust of [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] at [[Celebration IV]]. He also created a lifesize bust of Yoda at [[Celebration Europe (2007)|Celebration Europe]].

